name: FoxMind Maze Racers Game
category: Classic Board GamesEd Supplies & Early Childhood
discription:
Build, swap, and race!



Players or teams use magnetic walls and a good dose of creativity to build their mazes Tilt the ball through the maze as quick as you can in an effort to complete it first Two race boards, 79 magnetic obstacles, timer, start & finish loops, spacing checkers and balls Race boards measures 14-3/4” x 11”
